        <p>Whether you are using the default Central domain or host mapped domains (or both), any of the sites that you create can be associated with any of the domains on the URLs page view<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.Online-Only"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Central/Sites/Sites-Page-View/Main-Activities/Creating-Sites.htm">Creating Sites</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.Print-Only"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Print-Only-Topics/Central/Sites/Creating-Sites.htm">Creating Sites</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>. You can associate each site with a different domain, or you can associate multiple sites with the same domain. It's up to you.</p>
